{
  "text": "The MALvern Program Analysis Suite (Malpas) is a toolset for the analysis of software programs [CITATION_1] . Though this is primarily a static analysis tool, it can also provide a rigorous check that a program meets a specification. The program to be analyzed has to be in the Malpas Intermediate Language. In practice, this is easier than it sounds as there are automated translators from common programming languages and assembly languages to the Malpas Intermediate Language.",
